snippet.title: Cash Deficit and Long Queues outside ATMs Continue on Sunday

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Cash deficit and long queues outside ATMs continue on Sunday. Banks are closed this weekend and hence peoples are depend on ATMs only for cash withdrawal.
